org.batfish.grammar.juniper

Interface JuniperParserListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    JuniperFlattener, JuniperParserBaseListener

    public interface JuniperParserListener
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by JuniperParser.
